      "lineNumber": 1,
      "text": "Letter to Bureau",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 2,
      "text": "August 13, 1947",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 3,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 4,
      "text": "[REDACTED] upon interview",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 5,
      "text": "by Special Agent [REDACTED] stated that the event in question occurred",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 6,
      "text": "at about 7:30 on the evening of Sunday, August 3. She said that she",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 7,
      "text": "was in the house when [REDACTED] called to her. She went out",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 8,
      "text": "immediately, and they pointed out the object in question. She saw",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9,
      "text": "it just before it disappeared over the horizon, but she declared that",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 10,
      "text": "it was in view from that time for approximately one minute. She said",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 11,
      "text": "it was round and silver-blue in color and appeared to be revolving.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 12,
      "text": "She said that she did not recall making any comment that it might have",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 13,
      "text": "been a bird and herself had no idea of what it could be. In view of",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 14,
      "text": "the distance from which she noticed it, she said that it could not",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 15,
      "text": "have been more than six inches in diameter but would have been much",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 16,
      "text": "larger if she had been near to it. [REDACTED] said that she had",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 17,
      "text": "never seen anything like it before.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 18,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 19,
      "text": "She said that across the street the [REDACTED]",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 20,
      "text": "daughter, were the only people sitting on the porch and she, herself,",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 21,
      "text": "did not notice anyone pointing toward the object in question. The",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 22,
      "text": "only other person around, to her knowledge, was [REDACTED] sister",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 23,
      "text": "of [REDACTED] who remained in the house and did not see the object",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 24,
      "text": "at all.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 25,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 26,
      "text": "[REDACTED] stated that she",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 27,
      "text": "was on the porch on the evening in question with her mother but did",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 28,
      "text": "not notice any unusual object in the sky nor had any man been present",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 29,
      "text": "there to point out the object in question.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 30,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
